    <!-- Security notes -->
    <mxCell id="sec_note" value="Security Controls Summary&#xa;&#xa;• gRPC Server binds to 127.0.0.1 / private IP only (never 0.0.0.0)&#xa;• Kubernetes Service type: ClusterIP (no NodePort / LoadBalancer / Ingress)&#xa;• NetworkPolicy: only client pod allowed inbound on :50051&#xa;• mTLS: private CA (cert-manager), validate client cert CN/SAN&#xa;• gRPC Server Reflection: DISABLED in production&#xa;• Firewall: block gRPC port from outside subnet (defense in depth)&#xa;• Kafka: server connects outbound only; Kafka in separate namespace" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=1;fillColor=#f8cecc;strokeColor=#b85450;fontSize=9;" vertex="1" parent="1">
